mk-cad
======

This project depends on:

- build123d (https://github.com/gumyr/build123d), Apache License 2.0.
  Consumed via pip; not vendored.
- OCP (https://github.com/CadQuery/OCP), Apache License 2.0.
  Consumed transitively via build123d.
- OpenCascade Technology (https://github.com/Open-Cascade-SAS/OCCT),
  LGPL 2.1 with exception. Consumed transitively via OCP.
- yacv / yet-another-cad-viewer (https://github.com/yeicor-3d/yet-another-cad-viewer).
  Consumed unmodified as a sidecar container.

Vendored components:

- ltree.so — SQLite ltree extension (this user's own work).
- vendor/kb_python/ — KnowledgeBaseManager + Construct_KB classes
  (this user's own work, copied verbatim from
   ~/knowledge_base/kb_modules/kb_python/sqlite3/construct_kb/).
